OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FConjoined twins separated  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith the help of VR        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Brazilian twins who were joined at the 
OL,6, head have been successfully separated  
OL,7, with the help of virtual reality.      
OL,9,FThree-year-olds Bernardo and Arthur    
OL,10,FLima underwent surgeries in Rio de     
OL,11,FJaneiro, with direction from Great     
OL,12,FOrmond Street Hospital in London.      
OL,14,FThe teams spent months trialling       
OL,15,Ftechniques using virtual reality       
OL,16,Fprojections of the twins, based on CT  
OL,17,Fand MRI scans.                         
OL,19,FIt was described by surgeon Noor ul    
OL,20,FOwase Jeelani as "space-age stuff".    
